data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that exudes warmth and character from the moment you step onto the rocking chair front porch! Upon entering, you're greeted by a bright and inviting living area adorned with a vaulted ceiling, creating an airy atmosphere that feels like home. The seamless flow leads you from the living space to a dining area and well appointed kitchen, where stainless steel appliances await the culinary enthusiast in you. The bedrooms are bathed in natural light, creating a serene and welcoming retreat for restful nights. Each room is thoughtfully designed to maximize space and comfort, providing a perfect canvas for personalization. Both bathrooms feature a tub/shower combo for relaxation and convenience. The vanities with ample storage ensure that your daily routines are both elegant and organized. The fenced back yard is spacious, ideal for entertaining and furry friends. This home boasts charming details, spacious layout, and delightful features, don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
